===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# {{lb|zh|literary}} to [[look forward to]]; to [[hope]] [[for]]; to [[wish]]
#: {{zh-x|市民 冀 減少 交通 時間|Citizen(s) '''hope(s) for''' reduced travel time}}
#: {{zh-x|議員 冀 調節 經濟 援助 措施|Lawmaker(s) '''hope(s) for''' regulating financial aid measures}}
#* {{zh-x|因 釋 其 耒 而 守 株，冀 復 得 兔。|Thereupon [the farmer] laid aside his plow and [took up] watching the stump, '''hoping''' that he will get another rabbit [in the same way]. |CL|ref='''3rd century BC''', {{lw|zh|韓非}} ({{w|Han Fei}}), [[守株待兔]] (“Guarding Tree Stump to Wait For Rabbit”)}}
#* {{zh-x|君子 義 則 有 常，善 則 有 鄰；見 其 一，冀 其 二；見 其 小，冀 其 大；苟 有 德 焉，亦 不 求 盈 於 人 也。|A gentleman's righteousness will bring habit, and his kindness will bring neighborhood; when he sees one, he '''hopes for''' two; when he sees small, he '''hopes for''' big; even if he has virtue, he does not seek for abundance from others.|CL|ref={{w|Western Han}}, {{lw|zh|禮記}} ({{w|Book of Rites}}), {{lw|zh|s:大戴禮記/曾子立事|大戴禮記/曾子立事}} (“Da Dai Liji/Zengzi about the correct serving [one's superiors]”)}}
# {{zh-alt-name|河北|[[Hebei]], a [[province]] of China}}
#* {{zh-x|自是，冀 之 南，漢 之 陰，無 隴 斷 焉。||CL|ref={{w|Warring States}}, {{lw|zh|列禦寇}} ({{w|Lie Yukou}}), {{lw|zh|列子 (古籍)}} ({{w|Liezi}}), {{lw|zh|s:列子/湯問篇|列子/湯問篇}}}}
